Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.47,Love Asteroid - Default,Suzu,0,0,0,,Hở? Có chuyện gì thế, Mira?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.68,0:02:40.81,Love Asteroid - Default,Mira,0,0,0,,Suzu-chan!
