Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:34.68,Love Asteroid - Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Mình cũng thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:40.02,Love Asteroid - Default,Ao,0,0,0,,Mình đã luôn mong gặp lại cậu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.44,Love Asteroid - Default,Mira,0,0,0,,Ừm.
